</div>
<div aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute;left:94.93478260869566%;width:3.6304347826086936%;top:0;height:100%;background:#22c55e;opacity:0.85">
</div>
<div aria-hidden="true" title="Now" style="position:absolute;right:0;top:0;width:3px;height:100%;background:#ef4444">
</div>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:11px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);margin-top:4px">
<span>⟵ 4.6 billion years ago</span>
<span>now ⟶</span>
</div>
<div style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);font-style:italic;margin-top:4px">The whole age of dinosaurs is that green sliver near the far right. Everything before it is the long empty stretch.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:rgba(168,85,247,0.10);border:1px solid rgba(168,85,247,0.35);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);margin-bottom:12px">
<div style="font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.6">Squeeze all 4.6 billion years of Earth’s history into <strong>a single calendar year</strong>. Then:</div>
<ul style="margin:8px 0 0;padding-left:18px;font-size:13px;line-height:1.65">
<li>🦕 The first dinosaurs show up on <strong>December 13, 12:17 PM</strong>.</li>
<li>They rule for about <strong>13 days</strong>, until the asteroid on <strong>December 26, 6:18 PM</strong>.</li>
<li>🧑 Our species appears only in the very last <strong>34 minutes</strong>.</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:800;margin:4px 0 6px">Every big moment, in order</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;padding:6px 8px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:4px;background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155)">
<span aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:16px;width:22px;text-align:center">🌍</span>
<span style="flex:1;font-size:13px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Earth forms</span>
<span style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);min-width:90px;text-align:right">4.6 billion yrs</span>
<span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);min-width:130px;text-align:right">January 1</span>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;padding:6px 8px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:4px;background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155)">
<span aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:16px;width:22px;text-align:center">🦠</span>
<span style="flex:1;font-size:13px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">First life — simple microbes</span>
<span style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);min-width:90px;text-align:right">3.8 billion yrs</span>
<span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);min-width:130px;text-align:right">March 5</span>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;padding:6px 8px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:4px;background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155)">
<span aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:16px;width:22px;text-align:center">🫧</span>
<span style="flex:1;font-size:13px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Microbes fill the air with oxygen</span>
<span style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);min-width:90px;text-align:right">2.4 billion yrs</span>
<span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);min-width:130px;text-align:right">June 24</span>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;padding:6px 8px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:4px;background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155)">
<span aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:16px;width:22px;text-align:center">🔬</span>
<span style="flex:1;font-size:13px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">First complex (eukaryotic) cells</span>
<span style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);min-width:90px;text-align:right">1.8 billion yrs</span>
<span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);min-width:130px;text-align:right">August 11</span>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;padding:6px 8px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:4px;background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155)">
<span aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:16px;width:22px;text-align:center">🪼</span>
<span style="flex:1;font-size:13px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">First animals</span>
<span style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);min-width:90px;text-align:right">600 mya</span>
<span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);min-width:130px;text-align:right">November 14</span>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;padding:6px 8px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:4px;background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155)">
<span aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:16px;width:22px;text-align:center">🦐</span>
<span style="flex:1;font-size:13px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Cambrian explosion — animals diversify</span>
<span style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);min-width:90px;text-align:right">538 mya</span>
<span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);min-width:130px;text-align:right">November 19</span>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;padding:6px 8px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:4px;background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155)">
<span aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:16px;width:22px;text-align:center">🌿</span>
<span style="flex:1;font-size:13px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Plants spread onto land</span>
<span style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);min-width:90px;text-align:right">470 mya</span>
<span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);min-width:130px;text-align:right">November 24</span>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;padding:6px 8px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:4px;background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155)">
<span aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:16px;width:22px;text-align:center">🐟</span>
<span style="flex:1;font-size:13px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">First four-legged animals walk on land</span>
<span style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);min-width:90px;text-align:right">375 mya</span>
<span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);min-width:130px;text-align:right">December 2, 5:52 AM</span>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;padding:6px 8px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:4px;background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155)">
<span aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:16px;width:22px;text-align:center">🦎</span>
<span style="flex:1;font-size:13px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">First reptiles</span>
<span style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);min-width:90px;text-align:right">320 mya</span>
<span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);min-width:130px;text-align:right">December 6, 2:36 PM</span>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;padding:6px 8px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:4px;background:rgba(34,197,94,0.10);border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.30)">
<span aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:16px;width:22px;text-align:center">💀</span>
<span style="flex:1;font-size:13px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">The Great Dying (end-Permian extinction)</span>
<span style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);min-width:90px;text-align:right">252 mya</span>
<span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);min-width:130px;text-align:right">December 12, 12:06 AM</span>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;padding:6px 8px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:4px;background:rgba(34,197,94,0.10);border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.30)">
<span aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:16px;width:22px;text-align:center">🦕</span>
<span style="flex:1;font-size:13px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">First dinosaurs appear</span>
<span style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);min-width:90px;text-align:right">233 mya</span>
<span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);min-width:130px;text-align:right">December 13, 12:17 PM</span>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;padding:6px 8px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:4px;background:rgba(34,197,94,0.10);border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.30)">
<span aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:16px;width:22px;text-align:center">🐭</span>
<span style="flex:1;font-size:13px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">First mammals</span>
<span style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);min-width:90px;text-align:right">225 mya</span>
<span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);min-width:130px;text-align:right">December 14, 3:31 AM</span>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;padding:6px 8px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:4px;background:rgba(34,197,94,0.10);border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.30)">
<span aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:16px;width:22px;text-align:center">🪶</span>
<span style="flex:1;font-size:13px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">First birds (Archaeopteryx)</span>
<span style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);min-width:90px;text-align:right">150 mya</span>
<span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);min-width:130px;text-align:right">December 20, 2:20 AM</span>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;padding:6px 8px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:4px;background:rgba(34,197,94,0.10);border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.30)">
<span aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:16px;width:22px;text-align:center">☄️</span>
<span style="flex:1;font-size:13px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Asteroid — non-bird dinosaurs end</span>
<span style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);min-width:90px;text-align:right">66 mya</span>
<span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);min-width:130px;text-align:right">December 26, 6:18 PM</span>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;padding:6px 8px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:4px;background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155)">
<span aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:16px;width:22px;text-align:center">🐒</span>
<span style="flex:1;font-size:13px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">First human ancestors (hominins)</span>
<span style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);min-width:90px;text-align:right">7 mya</span>
<span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);min-width:130px;text-align:right">December 31, 10:40 AM</span>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;padding:6px 8px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:4px;background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155)">
<span aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:16px;width:22px;text-align:center">🧑</span>
<span style="flex:1;font-size:13px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">First Homo sapiens (us)</span>
<span style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);min-width:90px;text-align:right">0.3 mya</span>
<span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);min-width:130px;text-align:right">December 31, 11:25 PM</span>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;padding:6px 8px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:4px;background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155)">
<span aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:16px;width:22px;text-align:center">📍</span>
<span style="flex:1;font-size:13px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Right now</span>
<span style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);min-width:90px;text-align:right">today</span>
<span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);min-width:130px;text-align:right">the stroke of midnight, Dec 31</span>
</div>
</div>
<div style="background:rgba(56,189,248,0.10);border:1px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.30);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);margin-top:12px">
<div style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.55">🦖 Your pick, <strong>T. rex</strong>, first appears around <strong>December 26, 2:30 PM</strong> (68–66 mya).</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);margin-top:12px">
<div style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">These dates are a teaching analogy, not exact. Ages are rounded to widely-cited estimates; “first” events mark the oldest good fossils we have, which new finds can push back.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>"
`;

exports[`Dino Lab — render per tab (golden master) > renders the dig tab (snapshot) 1`] = `
"<div style="min-height:100%;background:var(--allo-stem-canvas, #0f172a);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div role="tablist" aria-label="Dino Lab sections" style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;padding:10px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220)">
<button id="dinotab-explore" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🔍 Explore</button>
<button id="dinotab-timeline" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">⏳ Timeline</button>
<button id="dinotab-deeptime" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🕰️ Deep Time</button>
<button id="dinotab-sites" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🗺️ Sites</button>
<button id="dinotab-ecosystem" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🌍 Ecosystems</button>
<button id="dinotab-compare" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">⚖️ Compare</button>
<button id="dinotab-dig" role="tab" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:700;background:#15803d;color:#fff;white-space:nowrap">⛏️ Dig Site</button>
<button id="dinotab-classify" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🌳 Classify</button>
<button id="dinotab-birds" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🐦 Bird Link</button>
<button id="dinotab-extinction" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">☄️ Extinction</button>
<button id="dinotab-anatomy" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🦴 Anatomy</button>
<button id="dinotab-records" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🏆 Records</button>
<button id="dinotab-quiz" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🧠 Quiz</button>
<button id="dinotab-notes" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">📓 Field Notes</button>
<button id="dinotab-glossary" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">📖 Glossary</button>
</div>
<div id="dinopanel" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="dinotab-dig" style="padding:16px">
<div>
<div style="margin-bottom:12px">
<div style="font-size:18px;font-weight:800">⛏️ Excavate a fossil</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);margin-top:2px">Dig cells to uncover bones. Clues appear as you go. Then identify what you found.</div>
</div>
<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(0, 1fr);gap:16px">
<div>
<div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:8px">
