<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);margin-top:2px">Not all dinosaurs lived together. Each rock formation is a snapshot of one place and time. Pick a site to meet its whole community.</div>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px;margin-bottom:10px;max-height:132px;overflow-y:auto">
