</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:12px">These animals shared one place and time. Here, 16 plant-eaters and omnivores lived alongside 7 hunters. Biggest are listed first.</div>
