<button id="dinotab-sites" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🗺️ Sites</button>
<button id="dinotab-ecosystem" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🌍 Ecosystems</button>
<button id="dinotab-compare" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">⚖️ Compare</button>
<button id="dinotab-dig" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">⛏️ Dig Site</button>
<button id="dinotab-classify" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🌳 Classify</button>
<button id="dinotab-birds" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🐦 Bird Link</button>
<button id="dinotab-extinction" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">☄️ Extinction</button>
<button id="dinotab-anatomy" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🦴 Anatomy</button>
<button id="dinotab-records" role="tab" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:700;background:#15803d;color:#fff;white-space:nowrap">🏆 Records</button>
<button id="dinotab-quiz" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🧠 Quiz</button>
<button id="dinotab-notes" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">📓 Field Notes</button>
<button id="dinotab-glossary" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">📖 Glossary</button>
</div>
<div id="dinopanel" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="dinotab-records" style="padding:16px">
<div>
<div style="margin-bottom:12px">
<div style="font-size:18px;font-weight:800">🏆 Record holders</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);margin-top:2px">Biggest, smallest, strongest. Many of these are best estimates, since the very largest animals are known from incomplete skeletons.</div>
</div>
<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));gap:12px;margin-bottom:16px">
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;margin-bottom:2px">Longest predator</div>
<div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:4px">Spinosaurus</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">About 15 meters long, the longest known meat-eating dinosaur.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;margin-bottom:2px">Heaviest dinosaur</div>
<div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:4px">Argentinosaurus</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">A titanosaur estimated near 70 tonnes or more, among the largest land animals ever.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;margin-bottom:2px">Longest dinosaur</div>
<div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:4px">Supersaurus</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">A diplodocid that may have stretched past 30 meters from nose to tail.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;margin-bottom:2px">Longest neck</div>
<div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:4px">Mamenchisaurus</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">Some neck estimates reach about 15 meters, the longest of any animal.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;margin-bottom:2px">Longest claws</div>
<div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:4px">Therizinosaurus</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">Hand claws up to about a meter long, the longest of any known animal.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;margin-bottom:2px">Smallest (non-bird)</div>
<div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:4px">Microraptor and kin</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">Crow-sized four-winged gliders, among the smallest non-bird dinosaurs.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;margin-bottom:2px">Strongest bite</div>
<div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:4px">Tyrannosaurus</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">A bite force estimated near 35,000 newtons, the strongest of any known land animal.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;margin-bottom:2px">Biggest brain for its size</div>
<div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:4px">Troodon and small raptors</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">Some of the highest brain-to-body ratios among dinosaurs.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;margin-bottom:2px">First dinosaur named</div>
<div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:4px">Megalosaurus</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">Named in 1824, before the word &quot;dinosaur&quot; was coined in 1842.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;margin-bottom:2px">First color mapped</div>
<div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:4px">Sinosauropteryx</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">The first dinosaur whose color, a ginger-and-white tail, was worked out from fossils.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;margin-bottom:2px">Best soft-tissue preservation</div>
<div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:4px">Scipionyx</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">A baby with preserved internal organs, down to the intestines.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;margin-bottom:2px">Largest duck-bill</div>
<div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:4px">Shantungosaurus</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">A crestless hadrosaur up to about 15 meters long.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-weight:800;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:8px">👥 People who built the science</div>
<div>
<div style="padding:10px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);margin-bottom:8px">
<div style="font-weight:700;font-size:13px">Gideon Mantell<span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);font-weight:400;margin-left:6px">1790 to 1852</span>
</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5;margin-top:2px">Named Iguanodon in 1825, one of the first dinosaurs recognized.</div>
</div>
<div style="padding:10px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);margin-bottom:8px">
<div style="font-weight:700;font-size:13px">William Buckland<span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);font-weight:400;margin-left:6px">1784 to 1856</span>
</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5;margin-top:2px">Named Megalosaurus in 1824, the first dinosaur to be scientifically described.</div>
</div>
<div style="padding:10px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);margin-bottom:8px">
<div style="font-weight:700;font-size:13px">Richard Owen<span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);font-weight:400;margin-left:6px">1804 to 1892</span>
</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5;margin-top:2px">Coined the word &quot;Dinosauria&quot; in 1842 and helped found London’s Natural History Museum.</div>
</div>
<div style="padding:10px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);margin-bottom:8px">
<div style="font-weight:700;font-size:13px">Mary Anning<span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);font-weight:400;margin-left:6px">1799 to 1847</span>
</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5;margin-top:2px">A pioneering fossil hunter whose marine reptile finds shaped early paleontology, long underrecognized.</div>
</div>
<div style="padding:10px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);margin-bottom:8px">
<div style="font-weight:700;font-size:13px">Cope and Marsh<span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);font-weight:400;margin-left:6px">1800s</span>
</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5;margin-top:2px">Rivals whose &quot;Bone Wars&quot; named dozens of dinosaurs, with both great discoveries and reckless mistakes.</div>
</div>
<div style="padding:10px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);margin-bottom:8px">
<div style="font-weight:700;font-size:13px">Barnum Brown<span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);font-weight:400;margin-left:6px">1873 to 1963</span>
</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5;margin-top:2px">Discovered the first Tyrannosaurus rex and many other famous dinosaurs.</div>
</div>
<div style="padding:10px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);margin-bottom:8px">
<div style="font-weight:700;font-size:13px">John Ostrom<span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);font-weight:400;margin-left:6px">1928 to 2005</span>
</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5;margin-top:2px">Studied Deinonychus and revived the idea that birds are living dinosaurs.</div>
</div>
<div style="padding:10px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);margin-bottom:8px">
<div style="font-weight:700;font-size:13px">Jack Horner<span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);font-weight:400;margin-left:6px">born 1946</span>
</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5;margin-top:2px">Found Maiasaura nesting grounds, transforming ideas about dinosaur parenting.</div>
</div>
<div style="padding:10px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);margin-bottom:8px">
<div style="font-weight:700;font-size:13px">Luis and Walter Alvarez<span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);font-weight:400;margin-left:6px">1980</span>
</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5;margin-top:2px">Proposed the asteroid-impact cause of the K-Pg extinction, backed by the iridium layer.</div>
</div>
<div style="padding:10px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);margin-bottom:8px">
<div style="font-weight:700;font-size:13px">Paul Sereno<span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);font-weight:400;margin-left:6px">born 1957</span>
</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5;margin-top:2px">Named many dinosaurs across Africa and South America, including Nigersaurus and Suchomimus.</div>
</div>
<div style="padding:10px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);margin-bottom:8px">
<div style="font-weight:700;font-size:13px">Xu Xing<span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);font-weight:400;margin-left:6px">born 1969</span>
</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5;margin-top:2px">Named more dinosaurs than almost anyone, many of them feathered, from China.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>"
`;

exports[`Dino Lab — render per tab (golden master) > renders the sites tab (snapshot) 1`] = `
"<div style="min-height:100%;background:var(--allo-stem-canvas, #0f172a);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div role="tablist" aria-label="Dino Lab sections" style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;padding:10px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220)">
<button id="dinotab-explore" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🔍 Explore</button>
<button id="dinotab-timeline" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">⏳ Timeline</button>
<button id="dinotab-deeptime" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🕰️ Deep Time</button>
<button id="dinotab-sites" role="tab" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:700;background:#15803d;color:#fff;white-space:nowrap">🗺️ Sites</button>
<button id="dinotab-ecosystem" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🌍 Ecosystems</button>
<button id="dinotab-compare" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">⚖️ Compare</button>
<button id="dinotab-dig" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">⛏️ Dig Site</button>
<button id="dinotab-classify" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🌳 Classify</button>
<button id="dinotab-birds" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🐦 Bird Link</button>
<button id="dinotab-extinction" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">☄️ Extinction</button>
<button id="dinotab-anatomy" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🦴 Anatomy</button>
<button id="dinotab-records" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🏆 Records</button>
<button id="dinotab-quiz" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🧠 Quiz</button>
<button id="dinotab-notes" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">📓 Field Notes</button>
<button id="dinotab-glossary" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">📖 Glossary</button>
</div>
<div id="dinopanel" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="dinotab-sites" style="padding:16px">
<div>
<div style="margin-bottom:12px">
<div style="font-size:18px;font-weight:800">🗺️ Famous fossil sites</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);margin-top:2px">Certain rock formations, laid down in the right place at the right time, hold most of what we know.</div>
</div>
<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));gap:12px">
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-weight:800;font-size:14px">📍 Hell Creek Formation</div>
<div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);margin-bottom:6px">USA (Montana, Dakotas)  ·  latest Cretaceous, ~68 to 66 mya</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;margin-bottom:4px">
<strong style="color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Famous for: </strong>T. rex, Triceratops, Ankylosaurus, Edmontosaurus</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">A window onto the very last days of the non-bird dinosaurs, right up to the K-Pg layer.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-weight:800;font-size:14px">📍 Morrison Formation</div>
<div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);margin-bottom:6px">USA (western states)  ·  Late Jurassic, ~155 to 145 mya</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;margin-bottom:4px">
<strong style="color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Famous for: </strong>Allosaurus, Stegosaurus, Brachiosaurus, Diplodocus</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">The classic American &quot;dinosaur graveyard&quot; of the Jurassic giants.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-weight:800;font-size:14px">📍 Dinosaur Park Formation</div>
<div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);margin-bottom:6px">Canada (Alberta)  ·  Late Cretaceous, ~77 to 75 mya</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;margin-bottom:4px">
<strong style="color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Famous for: </strong>Gorgosaurus, Centrosaurus, Corythosaurus, Styracosaurus</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">One of the richest dinosaur fossil areas in the world.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-weight:800;font-size:14px">📍 Yixian Formation (Jehol)</div>
<div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);margin-bottom:6px">China (Liaoning)  ·  Early Cretaceous, ~125 mya</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;margin-bottom:4px">
<strong style="color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Famous for: </strong>Sinosauropteryx, Microraptor, Yutyrannus, Psittacosaurus</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">Fine volcanic ash preserved feathers and even color. It transformed how we see dinosaurs.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-weight:800;font-size:14px">📍 Nemegt Formation</div>
<div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);margin-bottom:6px">Mongolia (Gobi Desert)  ·  Late Cretaceous, ~71 to 69 mya</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;margin-bottom:4px">
<strong style="color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Famous for: </strong>Tarbosaurus, Deinocheirus, Gallimimus, Therizinosaurus</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">A river-and-floodplain world that preserved many strange Asian dinosaurs.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-weight:800;font-size:14px">📍 Djadochta Formation</div>
<div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);margin-bottom:6px">Mongolia (Gobi Desert)  ·  Late Cretaceous, ~75 to 71 mya</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;margin-bottom:4px">
<strong style="color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Famous for: </strong>Velociraptor, Protoceratops, Oviraptor, Citipati</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">An ancient desert that froze behavior in time, including the Fighting Dinosaurs.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-weight:800;font-size:14px">📍 Solnhofen Limestone</div>
<div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);margin-bottom:6px">Germany (Bavaria)  ·  Late Jurassic, ~150 mya</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;margin-bottom:4px">
<strong style="color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Famous for: </strong>Archaeopteryx, Compsognathus</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">A still lagoon whose fine limestone preserved feathers in stunning detail.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-weight:800;font-size:14px">📍 Kem Kem Beds</div>
<div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);margin-bottom:6px">Morocco (Sahara)  ·  mid-Cretaceous, ~99 mya</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;margin-bottom:4px">
<strong style="color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Famous for: </strong>Spinosaurus, Carcharodontosaurus, Suchomimus</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">A river system that somehow supported several giant predators at once.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-weight:800;font-size:14px">📍 Ischigualasto Formation</div>
<div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);margin-bottom:6px">Argentina  ·  Late Triassic, ~231 mya</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;margin-bottom:4px">
<strong style="color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Famous for: </strong>Herrerasaurus, Eoraptor</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">The &quot;Valley of the Moon&quot;, recording the dawn of the dinosaurs.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-weight:800;font-size:14px">📍 Tendaguru Beds</div>
<div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);margin-bottom:6px">Tanzania  ·  Late Jurassic, ~152 mya</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;margin-bottom:4px">
<strong style="color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Famous for: </strong>Giraffatitan, Kentrosaurus</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">An African match to the Morrison, excavated in huge early expeditions.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-weight:800;font-size:14px">📍 Two Medicine Formation</div>
<div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);margin-bottom:6px">USA (Montana)  ·  Late Cretaceous, ~77 mya</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;margin-bottom:4px">
<strong style="color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Famous for: </strong>Maiasaura, Daspletosaurus, Einiosaurus</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">Egg Mountain here proved dinosaurs nested in colonies and cared for young.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="font-weight:800;font-size:14px">📍 Kaiparowits Formation</div>
<div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);margin-bottom:6px">USA (Utah)  ·  Late Cretaceous, ~76 to 74 mya</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;margin-bottom:4px">
<strong style="color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Famous for: </strong>Kosmoceratops, Nasutoceratops</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.5">A remote site revealing the lost southern world of the continent Laramidia.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>"
`;

exports[`Dino Lab — render per tab (golden master) > renders the timeline tab (snapshot) 1`] = `
"<div style="min-height:100%;background:var(--allo-stem-canvas, #0f172a);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div role="tablist" aria-label="Dino Lab sections" style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;padding:10px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220)">
<button id="dinotab-explore" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🔍 Explore</button>
<button id="dinotab-timeline" role="tab" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:700;background:#15803d;color:#fff;white-space:nowrap">⏳ Timeline</button>
<button id="dinotab-deeptime" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🕰️ Deep Time</button>
<button id="dinotab-sites" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🗺️ Sites</button>
<button id="dinotab-ecosystem" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🌍 Ecosystems</button>
<button id="dinotab-compare" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">⚖️ Compare</button>
<button id="dinotab-dig" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">⛏️ Dig Site</button>
<button id="dinotab-classify" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🌳 Classify</button>
<button id="dinotab-birds" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🐦 Bird Link</button>
<button id="dinotab-extinction" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">☄️ Extinction</button>
<button id="dinotab-anatomy" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🦴 Anatomy</button>
<button id="dinotab-records" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🏆 Records</button>
<button id="dinotab-quiz" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">🧠 Quiz</button>
<button id="dinotab-notes" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">📓 Field Notes</button>
<button id="dinotab-glossary" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="dinopanel" style="padding:7px 11px;border-radius:9px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;background:transparent;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);white-space:nowrap">📖 Glossary</button>
</div>
<div id="dinopanel" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="dinotab-timeline" style="padding:16px">
<div>
<div style="margin-bottom:12px">
<div style="font-size:18px;font-weight:800">⏳ Walk the Mesozoic</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);margin-top:2px">The &quot;age of dinosaurs&quot; spans more than 180 million years. Bar width shows how long each period lasted.</div>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--allo-stem-panel, #1e293b);border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">
<div style="margin-bottom:14px">
<div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap">
<span style="width:12px;height:12px;border-radius:3px;background:#a855f7;display:inline-block">
</span>
<span style="font-weight:800;font-size:15px">Triassic</span>
<span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">252 to 201 million years ago</span>
</div>
<div style="height:10px;border-radius:6px;background:#a855f733;margin:6px 0;overflow:hidden">
<div style="height:100%;width:22%;background:#a855f7">
</div>
</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);margin-bottom:4px">Dinosaurs appear, small and modest, late in the period.</div>
<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));gap:6px;margin-bottom:6px">
<div style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">🌡️ Hot and dry, with strong monsoons. One supercontinent, Pangaea.</div>
<div style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">🌿 Ferns, cycads, and early conifers. No flowering plants yet.</div>
<div style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">🌊 Panthalassa, a single world ocean, surrounded Pangaea.</div>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:5px">
<button aria-label="Open Coelophysis" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Coelophysis</button>
<button aria-label="Open Plateosaurus" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Plateosaurus</button>
<button aria-label="Open Herrerasaurus" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Herrerasaurus</button>
<button aria-label="Open Eoraptor" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Eoraptor</button>
<button aria-label="Open Tawa" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Tawa</button>
<button aria-label="Open Pisanosaurus" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Pisanosaurus</button>
<button aria-label="Open Riojasaurus" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Riojasaurus</button>
<button aria-label="Open Liliensternus" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Liliensternus</button>
<button aria-label="Open Eodromaeus" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Eodromaeus</button>
<button aria-label="Open Buriolestes" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Buriolestes</button>
<button aria-label="Open Antetonitrus" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Antetonitrus</button>
<button aria-label="Open Eocursor" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Eocursor</button>
<button aria-label="Open Lessemsaurus" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Lessemsaurus</button>
<button aria-label="Open Isanosaurus" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Isanosaurus</button>
<button aria-label="Open Melanorosaurus" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Melanorosaurus</button>
<button aria-label="Open Mussaurus" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Mussaurus</button>
</div>
</div>
<div style="margin-bottom:14px">
<div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap">
<span style="width:12px;height:12px;border-radius:3px;background:#0ea5e9;display:inline-block">
</span>
<span style="font-weight:800;font-size:15px">Jurassic</span>
<span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">201 to 145 million years ago</span>
</div>
<div style="height:10px;border-radius:6px;background:#0ea5e933;margin:6px 0;overflow:hidden">
<div style="height:100%;width:24%;background:#0ea5e9">
</div>
</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);margin-bottom:4px">The age of giant sauropods and the first birds.</div>
<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));gap:6px;margin-bottom:6px">
<div style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">🌡️ Warmer and wetter as Pangaea began to split apart.</div>
<div style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">🌿 Lush conifer forests, ginkgoes, tree ferns, and cycads.</div>
<div style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">🌊 New seaways opened as the Atlantic began to form.</div>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:5px">
<button aria-label="Open Stegosaurus" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Stegosaurus</button>
<button aria-label="Open Brachiosaurus" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Brachiosaurus</button>
<button aria-label="Open Allosaurus" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Allosaurus</button>
<button aria-label="Open Apatosaurus" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Apatosaurus</button>
<button aria-label="Open Archaeopteryx" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Archaeopteryx</button>
<button aria-label="Open Diplodocus" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Diplodocus</button>
<button aria-label="Open Compsognathus" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Compsognathus</button>
<button aria-label="Open Dilophosaurus" style="font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--allo-stem-border, #334155);background:var(--allo-stem-deeper, #0b1220);color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9)">Dilophosaurus</button>
