</div>
<div style="margin-bottom:14px">
<div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap">
<span style="width:12px;height:12px;border-radius:3px;background:#f59e0b;display:inline-block">
</span>
<span style="font-weight:800;font-size:15px">Paleogene</span>
<span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">66 to 23 million years ago</span>
</div>
<div style="height:10px;border-radius:6px;background:#f59e0b33;margin:6px 0;overflow:hidden">
<div style="height:100%;width:19%;background:#f59e0b">
</div>
</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);margin-bottom:4px">Non-bird dinosaurs are gone; birds and mammals diversify.</div>
<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));gap:6px;margin-bottom:6px">
<div style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">🌡️ Recovering after the impact; warm, then slowly cooling.</div>
<div style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">🌿 Forests recover; grasses begin to spread later on.</div>
<div style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8)">🌊 Seaways drained as continents took on modern shapes.</div>
</div>
<div style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);font-style:italic">No non-bird dinosaurs after the asteroid. Birds carry on.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="background:rgba(168,85,247,0.10);border:1px solid rgba(168,85,247,0.35);border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:var(--allo-stem-text, #f1f5f9);margin-top:12px">
<div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px">🤯 Deep time check</div>
<div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--allo-stem-text-soft, #94a3b8);line-height:1.55">Stegosaurus (about 150 million years ago) lived closer in time to you than to Tyrannosaurus (about 66 million years ago).</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>"
